      "number": "1",
      "text": "Required Adventures",
      "children": [
        {
          "number": "1",
          "text": "Bobcat Adventure",
          "children": [
            {
              "number": "1",
              "text": "Get to know members of your den."
            },
            {
              "number": "2",
              "text": "Recite the Scout Oath and the Scout Law with your den and den leader.  Describe the three points of the Scout Oath."
            },
            {
              "number": "3",
              "text": "Learn about the Scout Law."
            },
            {
              "number": "4",
              "text": "With your den create a den Code of Conduct."
            },
            {
              "number": "5",
              "text": "Learn about the denner position and responsibilities."
            },
            {
              "number": "6",
              "text": "Demonstrate the Cub Scout sign, Cub Scout salute and Cub Scout handshake.  Show how each is used."
            },
            {
              "number": "7",
              "text": "At home, with your parent or legal guardian do the activities in the booklet “How to Protect Your Children from Child Abuse: A Parent’s Guide.”"
            }
